            "body": "@superatomic Definitely smells related! I'm not confident it is, though. I can reproduce with this `init.lua`\n\n```\nrequire('vim._core.ui2').enable()\n-- Set the titlestring to the old default\nvim.opt.titlestring = '%t%( %M%)%( (%{expand(\"%:~:h\")})%)%a - Nvim'\nvim.opt.title = true\n```\n\nEDIT: yeah seems like this also happens on f2cc0a249d20462619801a194b67f6ab1d48476c, which is an ancestor to that commit.\n\nEntirely possible I'm missing something though...",
